snippet.title: Sudoku Universe - Nintendo Switch Trailer
snippet.description:
Publisher indienova and Konstructors Entertainment have announced that Sudoku Universe arrives on Nintendo Switch on August 8, 2019.

Sudoku Universe is basically what you expect from a sudoku game, including 3 different modes, play it on Nintendo Switch any time anywhere.
